</li> <li> Providing resources for upcoming grid summer school for exercises related to <span class="twikiNewLink">PanDA<a href="/bin/edit/Management/PanDA?topicparent=Management.20101201AgendaMinutes" rel="nofollow" title="PanDA (this topic does not yet exist; you can create it)">?</a></span>
